de.unifrankfurt.informatik.acoli.starling.parser

Interface StarlingParserI

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    StarlingParser

    public interface StarlingParserI
    Implement methods to parse complex information stored in a single string in XML fields of a record in a Starling XML dictionary.
    Author:
    frank
